#: data/io.github.virinvictus.atrium.gschema.xml:12
msgid ""
"Simple Mode shows the calm Things-3-style surface; Builder Mode adds the "
"Inspector pane, Forecast, Review, and Perspectives. Flipping mode is a UI re-"
"render only — the database is never touched (spec §3.1, \"Mode-as-View\")."
msgstr ""
"Simple Mode shows the calm Things-3-style surface; Builder Mode adds the "
"Inspector pane, Forecast, Review, and Perspectives. Flipping mode is a UI re-"
"render only — the database is never touched (spec §3.1, \"Mode-as-View\")."

